description:
Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj is a name that commands respect like no one else in Maharashtra & beyond…. Yet absolute silence from some quarters after the shocking collapse of Shivaji Maharaj’s statue (that was inaugurated by Modi just last year)
Like promises of #AccheDin … the statue was hollow and supported by rusting iron beams. 
But Marathi Asmita does not get disrespected after this open insult to one of India’s tallest leaders? Will the Marathi Manoos not speak up because it’s not politically ‘convenient’ to do so? 
Social Media warriors also have gone underground.
